Olivia is a resilient single mother who has faced her fair share of challenges, but her unwavering determination and positive spirit have helped her persevere. Despite her limited financial resources, she tirelessly pursues her passion for holistic health and wellness, using her skills and knowledge to support her community.

Demographics:
Age: 44
