Shopping Habits:
Olivia's shopping habits reflect her holistic approach to life. She seeks out sustainable, ethically-sourced products that align with her values, such as organic clothing, eco-friendly household items, and locally-produced foods. When possible, she prefers to shop at thrift stores, secondhand shops, and community-based markets, where she can find unique, affordable items. Olivia is also an avid DIYer, often repurposing and upcycling materials to create her own personal care products and home decor.

